data.description: Price adjustment on this maintenance free beautiful townhome in the sought after Rolling Hills Ranch subdivision. Easy access to I-25, makes this a perfect location for commuting. The vaulted ceilings, large windows and a skylight in the great room provide a bright and spacious "welcome home" to all that enter.  Stainless steel appliances grace the kitchen area , eat at bar, desk nook and pantry. The updated cable stair railing  gives a updated contemporary feel.  This home has 2 large bedrooms: the primary suite has a huge closet. The full bath has been updated with granite counters, bowl sinks and a shower/jet tub. High quality carpets include customer orders. The laminate flooring on the main level provides ease of care. Enjoy the mountain views from the patio area with variable color theme lighting system.  The unfinished basement is open for future expansion with a rough-in bath area. A large shelving system above the garage door provides extra storage in this 2-car attached garage. A newer furnace, roof, water heater and active radon system gives you peace of mind.
